{"tid":706263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【當年今日】1972年6月18日 香港六一八雨災","createTime":"2018-06-17T18:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T18:40:33.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90a5788614ae9ed47cb86152b234ad23b3fe1bd0","tid":706263,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T18:23:08.000Z","msg":"兩大災區：<br />\n半山寶珊道、旭龢道、干德道<br />\n觀塘雞寮徙置區（今翠屏邨）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8pljEZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8pljEZ7.jpg&h=3e9bd471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3Ep5Ums.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3Ep5Ums.jpg&h=4988d8db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2016/08/07/hkfp-history-brief-visual-history-1972-deadly-kotewall-road-landslide/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2016%2F08%2F07%2Fhkfp-history-brief-visual-history-1972-deadly-kotewall-road-landslide%2F&d=b1NdBpQIGJllXdltVKfc7ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=4eca40a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2016/08/07/hkfp-history-brief-visual-history-1972-deadly-kotewall-road-landslide/</a><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://notcomment.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/618%E9%9B%A8%E7%81%BD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnotcomment.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F06%2F618%25E9%259B%25A8%25E7%2581%25BD.jpg&h=8986f5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i913.photobucket.com/albums/ac332/lvcatable/ec0891bc-d829-486c-8cb9-671b637a83aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi913.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fac332%2Flvcatable%2Fec0891bc-d829-486c-8cb9-671b637a83aa.jpg&h=00b5d871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/020849_8554c4b2d581339770304f95d84aa913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F020849_8554c4b2d581339770304f95d84aa913.jpg&h=4c7fa95c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/021410_cc2e74cd4ec1f18c050831ebd412333c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F021410_cc2e74cd4ec1f18c050831ebd412333c.jpg&h=a33a61c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/documents/19/8526189/1_03.jpg/ca72d3db-0786-4cae-aecb-d42cc97ac0c1?t=1444736442241\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmis.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fdocuments%2F19%2F8526189%2F1_03.jpg%2Fca72d3db-0786-4cae-aecb-d42cc97ac0c1%3Ft%3D1444736442241&h=f3ae90bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/documents/19/8526189/1_02.jpg/b93d8f10-ef8f-4ffc-9523-dc6bf66fd59f?t=1444736442005\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmis.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fdocuments%2F19%2F8526189%2F1_02.jpg%2Fb93d8f10-ef8f-4ffc-9523-dc6bf66fd59f%3Ft%3D1444736442005&h=e3f0b0df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/zh/kt_03\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmis.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fzh%2Fkt_03&d=b1NdBpQIGJllXdltVKfc7ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=39adfa55\" target=\"_blank\">https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/zh/kt_03</a><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u89mD1dMSGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du89mD1dMSGM&d=b1NdBpQIGJllXdltVKfc7ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=675cfd8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u89mD1dMSGM</a><br />\n香港故事(第15輯) 打風落雨:韋基舜憶述618雨災"},{"pid":"3e894d5ed5ed91355f3d61df1ada4ad2f0f86d76","tid":706263,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T18:24:57.000Z","msg":"成棟冧真係誇張"},{"pid":"315b3b5cc69d465ef19855b0ccc8fefee0456ddc","tid":706263,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e894d5ed5ed91355f3d61df1ada4ad2f0f86d76","tid":706263,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T18:24:57.000Z","msg":"成棟冧真係誇張"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T18:31:57.000Z","msg":"1972年的6月18日雨災，便導致觀塘翠屏木屋區旁山泥傾瀉，港島半山區寶珊道一幢12層高樓宇更被山泥沖塌，整場雨災共造成156人死亡、117人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n1972年6月16日起，香港大雨連場，居於觀塘安置區的居民，在暴雨首日已擔心木屋區附近的建築地盤泥土有滑坡風險，當時警方接報到場後，曾勒令地盤須確保泥土不再下瀉。然而，到了6月18日，山泥終抵受不住暴雨沖刷而下塌。<br />\n<br />\n6月18日下午約1時，觀塘翠屏街的臨時木屋區的70多間木屋被大量因連日暴雨而沖下的山泥所淹蓋，過百居民當場被淹埋，部份木屋更被山泥推至觀塘新區。由於事發當日為星期日，加上多日來的連場暴雨，大批居民都未有外出，導致災情嚴重多人遭到活埋，事故造成71死52傷。<br />\n<br />\n除木屋區外，港島半山地區在這次雨災中亦不能倖免，港島區半山寶珊道亦因豪雨而發生山泥傾瀉，當日晚上約9時山坡上的山泥開始向下滑，首先沖毀一棟兩層高樓房，再將干德道一棟六層高樓宇沖毀，直衝當時新落成、樓高12層的旭和大廈，強大衝擊力令大廈全棟倒塌斷成多截。駐港英軍及消防員連夜搜救，救出不少生還者，包括根據收音機的歌聲而被救出的前大法官列顯倫。事故最終造成67死19傷，而倒塌的旭和大廈，是香港至今最多層數的倒塌的建築物。<br />\n<br />\n618雨災三日期間錄得652.3毫米雨量，造成過百人死傷，香港各界發起籌款賑災，無綫電視發起的賑災節目邀請梁醒波、譚炳文、許冠文、李小龍、陳寶珠、任劍輝、白雪仙及新馬師曾等當紅巨星作12小時馬拉松籌款，並共籌得900萬元為災民重建家園，金額亦打破當年賑災籌款的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140618/52578641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140618%2F52578641&d=b1NdBpQIGJllXdltVKfc7ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=67313e28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140618%2F52578641&h=5c323483\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140618/52578641</a>"},{"pid":"80675f7550b9ca15a8bf8d0e0bd3aea3cdd66b0f","tid":706263,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T18:40:33.000Z","msg":"六一八雨災電視籌款賑災節目<br />\n<br />\n任白、雛鳳義唱《李後主之去國歸降》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CMTGbJSMaq8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCMTGbJSMaq8&d=b1NdBpQIGJllXdltVKfc7ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=97e0cc63\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CMTGbJSMaq8</a><br />\n<br />\n任白義唱《帝女花之香夭》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9VDxQ7ZskPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9VDxQ7ZskPQ&d=b1NdBpQIGJllXdltVKfc7ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7f4918bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9VDxQ7ZskPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n麥炳榮、鳳凰女義唱《胡地蠻歌》(《鳳閣恩仇未了情》選段)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sbRmpfsLOfg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsbRmpfsLOfg&d=b1NdBpQIGJllXdltVKfc7ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3a5bb235\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sbRmpfsLOfg</a><br />\n<br />\n其餘片段，包括新馬師曾、陳寶珠義唱、李小龍表演截拳道<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aGCciSoAwIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaGCciSoAwIs&d=b1NdBpQIGJllXdltVKfc7ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6bea0109\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aGCciSoAwIs</a>"}]}